# Quatro Climate — Marketing Agent

AI-powered marketing dashboard for Quatro Climate. Built with Claude Sonnet.

## Deploy to Vercel (5 minutes)

### Step 1 — Push to GitHub
1. Go to github.com → New repository → name it `quatro-marketing-agent` → Create
2. Upload all these files (drag and drop, or use GitHub Desktop)

### Step 2 — Connect to Vercel
1. Go to vercel.com → Add New Project
2. Import your `quatro-marketing-agent` GitHub repo
3. Click Deploy (default settings are fine)

### Step 3 — Add your API key
1. In Vercel → your project → Settings → Environment Variables
2. Add:
   - **Name:** `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY`
   - **Value:** your Anthropic API key (from console.anthropic.com)
3. Click Save
4. Go to Deployments → click the three dots on latest deployment → Redeploy

### Step 4 — Done
Your app is live at `https://quatro-marketing-agent.vercel.app` (or similar).
Bookmark it. Share it with your team. It works from any browser.

## Project Structure
```
quatro-marketing-agent/
├── api/
│   └── proxy.js          ← Serverless function (holds API key securely)
├── public/
│   └── index.html        ← Full marketing agent UI
├── vercel.json           ← Vercel routing config
├── package.json
└── .gitignore
```

## Tools included
- SEO Audit (keyword targets, content gaps, meta tags, full audit)
- Competitor Intelligence (landscape, messaging, battle cards, objections)
- Content Studio (blog, LinkedIn, newsletter, case study)
- Outreach Emails (aviation, logistics, corporate)
- Pitch Deck Builder (slide-by-slide outlines with speaker notes)
- Contact Finder (Apollo · Hunter · LinkedIn queries)
- Tree Pledges & Nature (pledge packs, campaigns, social posts, FAQs)
